casebody.data:
FJN LLC, Gino's Surf, Franks Holding, LLC, Frank Nazar, Sr., and Frank Nazar, Jr. Plaintiffs-Appellants,
v.
Vijay PARAKH and Charter Township of Harrison, Defendants-Appellees. SC: 156224
COA: 331889 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 29, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's February 20, 2018 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because it does not appear that the order was entered erroneously.

Viviano, J., not participating due to a familial relationship with the presiding circuit court judge in this case.
